item.title: CVE-2019-6628|2024-08-04T20:23:22.324Z -- f5 -- big-ip%20pem
item.description: On BIG-IP PEM 14.1.0-14.1.0.5 and 14.0.0-14.0.0.4, under certain conditions, the TMM process may terminate and restart while processing BIG-IP PEM traffic with the OpenVPN classifier.
